data.description: Recently renovated 2 bed 2 bath condo in Lakewood featuring wood-style flooring throughout! Positioned uniquely adjacent to a creek and open space, providing ample privacy. Conveniently located near biking/walking trails, within walking distance to reservoirs, parks, and grocery stores. Just a brief drive to Green Mountain! Modernized kitchen equipped with stainless steel appliances, white cabinets, pantry, and tile backsplash. The main living area boasts an updated fireplace, living room, and dining area. Enjoy two patios, each with its own storage space, plus ample storage options indoors. Updated bathrooms and laundry area included! This unit comes with a one-car detached garage and an assigned parking spot. Community amenities include a pool and clubhouse.
